    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</span></p></td>
    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</span></p></td>
    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</span></p></td>
    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;min-width:fit-content;">Elizabeth O'Callahan<br/>Executive Vice President, Chief Legal Officer and Secretary</span></p></td>
   </tr>

  <title>EX-99.1</title>
 </head>
 <body style="margin: auto!important;padding: 8px;line-height: 1;">
  <div style="padding-top:0.5in;z-index:-3;min-height:0.38in;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div>
  <p style="margin-left:10%;text-indent:3.704%;font-size:10pt;margin-top:6pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:right;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:fit-content;">Exhibit 99.1</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:center;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp Reports Second Quarter of Fiscal Year 2025 Results</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Net revenues of $1.66 billion for the second quarter; 6% year-over-year increase</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:5.731%;text-align:center;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Record all-flash array annualized net revenue run rate</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">1</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> of $3.8 billion, an increase of 19% year-over-year</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">First party and marketplace cloud storage services revenue grew approximately 43% year-over-year</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Second quarter GAAP operating margin of 21%; record second quarter non-GAAP operating margin</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">2</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> of 29%</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Second quarter GAAP net income per share</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">3</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> of $1.42; record second quarter non-GAAP net income per share</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">2</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> of $1.87</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Returned $406 million to stockholders through share repurchases and cash dividends</font></div></div>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">SAN JOSE, Calif.&#x2014;November 21, 2024&#x2014;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today reported financial results for the second quarter of fiscal year 2025, which ended on October 25, 2024.</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#x201c;Our strong Q2 performance was driven by another record-breaking quarter in all-flash storage and strong performance in first party and marketplace cloud storage services,&#x201d; said George Kurian, chief executive officer. &#x201c;Broad-based customer preference for our intelligent data infrastructure platform and visionary approach for a data-driven future has enabled us to outgrow the market and take share from competitors. Our focus and momentum fuel my confidence in our ability to deliver outstanding results for customers and shareholders.&#x201d;</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:-1.709%;padding-left:1.667%;font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Second Quarter of Fiscal Year 2025 Financial Results</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:-1.709%;padding-left:1.667%;font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Net revenues:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> $1.66 billion, compared to $1.56 billion in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024; a year-over-year increase of 6%.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="margin-left:2.667%;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.9181572539631986%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">o</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Hybrid Cloud segment revenue:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> $1.49 billion, compared to $1.41 billion in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="margin-left:2.667%;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.9181572539631986%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">o</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Public Cloud segment revenue:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> $168 million, compared to $154 million in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Billings</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">2</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">: </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">$1.59 billion, compared to $1.45 billion in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024; a year-over-year increase of 9%. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">All-flash array ARR: </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">$3.8 billion, compared to $3.2 billion in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024; a year-over-year increase of 19%.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Net income:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> GAAP net income of $299 million, compared to $233 million in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024; non-GAAP net income</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">of $392 million, compared to $334 million in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Earnings per share:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> GAAP net income per share</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">of $1.42, compared to $1.10 in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024; non-GAAP net income per share of $1.87, compared to $1.58 in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024. </font></div></div>
  <div class="page-node-content"><div style="z-index:-3;flex-direction:column;display:flex;padding-bottom:0.5in;min-height:0.5in;justify-content:flex-end;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div></div>
  <hr style="margin-inline-start:auto;margin-inline-end:auto;page-break-after:always;">
  <div style="padding-top:0.5in;z-index:-3;min-height:0.38in;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Cash, cash equivalents and investments:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> $2.22 billion at the end of the second quarter of fiscal year 2025.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Cash provided by operations: </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">$105 million, compared to $135 million in the second quarter of fiscal year 2024.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Share repurchases and dividends: </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Returned $406 million to stockholders through share repurchases and cash dividends.</font></div></div>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Third Quarter of Fiscal Year 2025 Financial Outlook</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">The Company provided the following financial guidance for the third quarter of fiscal year 2025:</font></p>
  <table style="border-spacing:0;table-layout:fixed;width:95.0%;border-collapse:separate;">
   <tr style="visibility:collapse;">
    <td style="width:65%;box-sizing:content-box;"></td>
    <td style="width:18.86%;box-sizing:content-box;"></td>
    <td style="width:16.14%;box-sizing:content-box;"></td>
   </tr>
   <tr style="height:11pt;word-break:break-word;white-space:pre-wrap;">
    <td style="border-top:0.5pt solid #000000;padding-top:0in;border-right:0.5pt solid #000000;border-left:0.5pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.08in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;border-bottom:0.5pt solid #000000;padding-right:0.08in;"><p style="font-size:11pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Net revenues are expected to be in the range of:</font></p></td>
    <td colspan="2" style="border-top:0.5pt solid #000000;padding-top:0in;border-right:0.5pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.08in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;border-bottom:0.5pt solid #000000;padding-right:0.08in;text-align:left;"><p style="font-size:11pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:center;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">$1.610 billion - $1.760 billion</font></p></td>
   </tr>
   <tr style="height:11pt;word-break:break-word;white-space:pre-wrap;">
    <td style="padding-top:0in;border-right:0.5pt solid #000000;border-left:0.5pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.08in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;border-bottom:0.5pt solid #000000;padding-right:0.08in;"><p style="font-size:11pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p></td>

  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.926%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.926%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Leading Product Innovation</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#x202f;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.926%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp launched the new all-flash </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp&#153; ASA A-Series</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">storage systems</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> to enable simplicity, powerful high-end capabilities, and affordability for enterprise block storage. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp introduced new </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">midrange and high-end NetApp FAS hybrid flash storage arrays</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">, which deliver affordable, yet high-performing backup storage and enable a secure cyber vault for recovery from ransomware attacks.</font></div></div>
  <div class="page-node-content"><div style="z-index:-3;flex-direction:column;display:flex;padding-bottom:0.5in;min-height:0.5in;justify-content:flex-end;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div></div>
  <hr style="margin-inline-start:auto;margin-inline-end:auto;page-break-after:always;">
  <div style="padding-top:0.5in;z-index:-3;min-height:0.38in;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced its vision to accelerate AI innovation, including beginning the process of </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NVIDIA DGX SuperPOD Storage Certification for NetApp ONTAP&#153;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">, the creation of a </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">global metadata namespace</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">, a vision for a disaggregated storage architecture for ONTAP, and </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">direct integration of AI data pipelines</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> in the cloud and on-premises.  </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp unveiled new integrations with </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NVIDIA AI software,</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> combining NVIDIA NeMo Retriever and NIM microservices with intelligent data infrastructure to</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> accelerate enterprise retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) and to power agentic AI</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced enhancements to</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">its </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">cyber resilience offerings</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">, including the general availability of </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp ONTAP Autonomous Ransomware Protection with AI</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> and integrations of NetApp </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">BlueXP&#153; ransomware protection</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> with Splunk security information and event management (SIEM).</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp Keystone&#153; storage as a service (STaaS) incorporates NetApp Cloud Insights</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> into a single subscription model for comprehensive infrastructure intelligence. Customers get the flexibility to purchase the power of real-time analytics and monitoring for their entire environment&#x2014;both Keystone and non Keystone systems&#x2014;through a single Keystone subscription.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced that customers can now extend&#x202f;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp SnapMirror</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">&#153;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">replication</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> to integrate on-premises data with knowledge bases and to improve developer efficiency and data protection. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">The </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">FlexPod&#153; platform, a joint solution from NetApp and Cisco,</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> integrated </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp AFF A-Series</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">systems </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">to enhance performance and efficiency in data centers. With this integration, FlexPod delivers up to 2x greater performance than before, broad workload support, and advanced security features while maintaining reliable, scalable infrastructure for mission-critical applications. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced the general availability of </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp AIPod&#153; with Lenovo for NVIDIA OVX</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">, designed for enterprises that aim to harness generative AI and RAG capabilities to boost productivity, to streamline operations, and to unlock new revenue opportunities.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp updated </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp Cloud Volumes ONTAP </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">to include </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp ONTAP Autonomous Ransomware Protection</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">with AI (ARP/AI) </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">and </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">write once read many</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> (WORM) capabilities at no additional cost, strengthening IT teams&#x2019; ability to fight ransomware attacks.</font></div></div>

  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NVIDIA </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">announced plans to partner with U.S. technology leaders to help organizations create custom AI applications by using the latest </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NVIDIA NIM Agent Blueprints and NVIDIA NeMo and NVIDIA NIM microservices.</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> NetApp is among the partners to advance </font><font style="color:#1a1a1a;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">their data and AI platforms with NVIDIA NIM.</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Carahsoft Technology</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> entered into a </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">distributor agreement with NetApp to serve the</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">U.S. Public Sector</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">, making NetApp offerings available through Carahsoft&#x2019;s reseller partners and its NASA Solutions for Enterprise-Wide Procurement V and National Association of State Procurement Officials ValuePoint contracts. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">F5 </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">and NetApp announced an expanded collaboration to </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">accelerate and to streamline enterprise AI capabilities by </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">using </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">secure multicloud networking solutions</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> from F5 and the NetApp suite of data management solutions. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">has partnered with</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> DataNeuron</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> to simplify and to </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">reduce the cost of developing and scaling generative AI pipelines </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">through a no-code platform that integrates</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> retrieval-augmented generation and fine-tuning technologies</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> for customized, efficient AI solutions. </font></div></div>

  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp appointed</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;"> Mike Richardson </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">as </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">Vice President of U.S. Solutions Engineering</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">.   <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp will host a conference call to discuss these results today at 2:30 p.m. Pacific Time.
